Foxfingers looked down at the scarred maximal emblem on his chest, A 
constant reminder of a deal gone bad. "I'm undamaged, I would like to 
be shown around if you have the time. I haven't had the company of 
other translifeforms in ages. I think I'd like to meet everybody 
here." he looked Grimmler in the eyes,"And I look forward to all the 
new friends I will have here, starting with you." 

Foxfingers slaps Grimmler on the shoulder in a playful manner 
scratching a flake of metal into a compartment beneath his 
fingernails.

OOC what is Grimmlers beast mode, I may need it for future reference.
